<mart. 2.14.6>	si quid Phillyrides praestet et Aesonides.
<mart. 2.14.7>	Hic quoque deceptus Memphitica templa frequentat,
<mart. 2.14.8>	adsidet et cathedris, maesta iuvenca, tuis.
<mart. 2.14.9>	Inde petit centum pendentia tecta columnis,
<mart. 2.14.10>	illinc Pompei dona nemusque duplex.
<mart. 2.14.11>	Nec Fortunati spernit nec balnea Fausti,
<mart. 2.14.12>	nec Grylli tenebras Aeoliamque Lupi:
<mart. 2.14.13>	nam thermis iterumque iterumque iterumque lavatur.
<mart. 2.14.14>	Omnia cum fecit, sed renuente deo,
<mart. 2.14.15>	lotus ad Europes tepidae buxeta recurrit,
<mart. 2.14.16>	si quis ibi serum carpat amicus iter.
<mart. 2.14.17>	Per te perque tuam, vector lascive, puellam,
<mart. 2.14.18>	ad cenam Selium tu, rogo, taure, voca.

<mart. 2.16.1>	Zoilus aegrotat: faciunt hanc stragula febrem.
